title: Прусские коалиционные переговоры
view-if: prussia_coalition_trigger = 1
on-arrival: was_in_social_catholic_coalition_prussia = 0; was_in_social_liberal_coalition_prussia = 0; was_in_weimar_coalition_prussia = 0; was_in_grand_coalition_prussia = 0; was_in_social_catholic_coalition_prussia = 1 if in_social_catholic_coalition_prussia == 1 or in_minority_social_catholic_coalition_prussia == 1; was_in_social_liberal_coalition_prussia = 1 if in_social_liberal_coalition_prussia == 1 or in_minority_social_liberal_coalition_prussia == 1; was_in_weimar_coalition_prussia = 1 if ((in_weimar_coalition_prussia == 1 or in_minority_weimar_coalition_prussia == 1) or (in_grand_coalition_prussia == 1 and lvp_formed)); was_in_grand_coalition_prussia = 1 if (in_grand_coalition_prussia == 1 or in_minority_grand_coalition_prussia == 1); in_right_coalition_prussia = 0; in_social_catholic_coalition_prussia = 0; in_social_liberal_coalition_prussia = 0; in_weimar_coalition_prussia = 0; in_grand_coalition_prussia = 0; in_minority_grand_coalition_prussia = 0; in_popular_front_prussia = 0; in_left_front_prussia = 0; in_spd_majority_prussia = 0; in_center_right_coalition_prussia = 0; in_far_right_coalition_prussia = 0; in_minority_weimar_coalition_prussia = 0; in_minority_social_catholic_coalition_prussia = 0; in_minority_social_liberal_coalition_prussia = 0; spd_prussia = 0; right_prussia = 0; ddp_in_popular_front_prussia = 0; kpd_goals_seen_prussia = 0; spd_toleration_prussia = 0; prussia_coalition_trigger = 0
on-departure: {!
if (Q.in_social_catholic_coalition_prussia || Q.in_social_liberal_coalition_prussia || Q.in_weimar_coalition_prussia == 1 || Q.in_grand_coalition_prussia == 1 || Q.in_popular_front_prussia == 1 || Q.in_left_front_prussia == 1 || Q.in_spd_majority_prussia == 1 || Q.in_minority_weimar_coalition_prussia == 1 || Q.in_minority_grand_coalition_prussia == 1) {
    Q.spd_prussia = 1;
    Q.right_prussia = 0;
} else if (Q.in_right_coalition_prussia == 1 || Q.in_center_right_coalition_prussia == 1 || Q.prussia_leader == "Papen" || Q.prussia_leader == "Goring" || Q.in_far_right_coalition_prussia == 1) {
    Q.right_prussia = 1;
    Q.spd_prussia = 0;
}
!}
new-page: true
tags: event
priority: 1
face-image: img/prussia_flag_old.png
go-to: coalition_menu

= Формирование коалиции

Коалиционное правительство пало, и необходимо сформировать новое.


@coalition_menu

- @spd_majority
- @weimar_coalition_prussia
- @social_christian_coalition_prussia
- @social_liberal_coalition_prussia
- @minority_social_christian_coalition_prussia
- @minority_social_liberal_coalition_prussia
- @minority_weimar_coalition
- @grand_coalition_prussia
- @minority_grand_coalition_prussia
- @far_right_coalition_prussia
- @left_coalition_prussia
- @popular_front_coalition_prussia
- @right_coalition_prussia
- @center_right_coalition_prussia
- @bourgeois_coalition_prussia
- @bourgeois_coalition_kvp_prussia
- @call_new_elections: Будут назначены новые выборы.



@spd_majority
title: <span style="color: #c00000;">**СДПГ**</span> единоличное большинство
subtitle: <span style="color: #c00000;">**СДПГ**</span>: [+ spd_r_prussia +]%
view-if: spd_r_prussia >= 50
on-arrival: pro_republic += 5; reichswehr_loyalty -= 0.05 if chancellor == "Braun"; ddp_right += 2; dvp_right += 4; lvp_right += 3; liberal_cooperation += 5; bourgeois_cooperation += 5; prussia_leader = "Braun"; in_spd_majority_prussia = 1; prussian_police_loyalty += 0.1; prussian_police_strength += 50; democratization += 3; coup_progress += 1; capital_strike_progress += 2; ddp_relation -= 3; lvp_relation -= 3; z_relation -= 3; spd_prussia = 1

Наконец-то <span style="color: #c00000;">**СДПГ**</span> может править в одиночку! Наша долгая избирательная кампания принесла свои плоды. Нам больше не нужно думать о создании коалиции — теперь возможно всё. Однако наши бывшие партнёры по коалиции начнут смещаться вправо.

Браун избран министром-президентом Пруссии.



@social_christian_coalition_prussia
title: Сможем ли мы сформировать <span style="color: #c00000;">социал</span>-<span style="color: #000000;">христианскую</span> коалицию?
subtitle: <span style="color: #c00000;">**СДПГ**</span> + <span style="color: #000000;">**[+ z_party_name +]**</span> ([+ social_catholic_coalition_prussia +]%)
unavailable-subtitle: <span style="color: #c00000;">СДПГ</span> + <span style="color: #000000;">[+ z_party_name +]</span> ([+ social_catholic_coalition_prussia +]%) [? if far_right_coalition_prussia >= 50: - <span style="color: #7A3C00;">Крайне</span> <span style="color: #3E88B3;">правые</span> могут сформировать правительство. ?] [? if not ((z_relation >= 70 and cvp_ideology == "Moderate") or (z_relation >= 60 and cvp_ideology == "Left")): - У нас недостаточно хорошие отношения с <span style="color: #000000;">**ХНП**</span>. ?]
view-if: social_catholic_coalition_prussia >= 50 and cvp_formed
choose-if: far_right_coalition_prussia < 50 and ((z_relation >= 70 and cvp_ideology == "Moderate") or (z_relation >= 60 and cvp_ideology == "Left"))
on-arrival: in_social_catholic_coalition_prussia = 1; was_in_social_catholic_coalition_prussia = 1; prussia_leader = "Stegerwald" if cvp_leader != "Stegerwald"; prussia_leader = "Brüning" if z_leader == "Stegerwald"; pro_republic += 6; new_middle_z += 4; new_middle_spd += 2; z_relation += 5; reformist_dissent -= 10; spd_prussia = 1

Мы заручились достаточным количеством голосов, чтобы сформировать правительство «<span style="color: #c00000;">социал</span>-<span style="color: #000000;">христианской</span> коалиции», объединившее <span style="color: #c00000;">**СДПГ**</span> и <span style="color: #000000;">**ХНП**</span>. Неожиданно, благодаря нашим хорошим отношениям и относительно благоприятному руководству <span style="color: #000000;">**[+ z_party_name +]**</span>, мы успешно убедили их присоединиться к коалиции в Пруссии — регионе, где левое крыло партии <span style="color: #000000;">Центра</span> исторически имело значительное влияние.

[? if prussia_leader != "Braun": [+ prussia_leader +] избран министром-президентом Пруссии. ?]


@social_liberal_coalition_prussia
title: Мы можем сформировать <span style="color: #c00000;">социал</span>-[? if not lvp_formed: <span style="color: #D3C24D;">либеральную</span> ?][? if lvp_formed: <span style="color: #FFCC00;">либеральную</span> ?]коалицию.
subtitle: <span style="color: #c00000;">**СДПГ**</span> + [? if not lvp_formed: <span style="color: #D3C24D;">**[+ ddp_name +]**</span> ?][? if lvp_formed: <span style="color: #FFCC00;">**ЛНП**</span> ?] ([+ social_liberal_coalition_prussia +]%)
unavailable-subtitle: <span style="color: #c00000;">СДПГ</span> + [? if not lvp_formed: <span style="color: #D3C24D;">[+ ddp_name +]</span> ?][? if lvp_formed: <span style="color: #FFCC00;">ЛНП</span> ?] ([+ social_liberal_coalition_prussia +]%) [? if far_right_coalition_prussia >= 50: - <span style="color: #7A3C00;">Крайне</span> <span style="color: #3E88B3;">правые</span> могут сформировать правительство. ?] [? if not ((ddp_relation >= 60 and ddp_ideology == "Right") or (ddp_relation >= 50 and ddp_ideology == "Moderate") or (ddp_relation >= 40 and ddp_ideology == "Left")) and not lvp_formed: - У нас нет надлежащих отношений с <span style="color: #D3C24D;">[+ ddp_name +]</span>. ?] [? if not ((lvp_relation >= 70 and lvp_ideology == "Right") or (lvp_relation >= 60 and lvp_ideology == "Moderate") or (lvp_relation >= 50 and lvp_ideology == "Left")) and lvp_formed: - У нас недостаточно хорошие отношения с <span style="color: #FFCC00;">ЛНП</span>. ?]
view-if: social_liberal_coalition_prussia >= 50 and cvp_formed
choose-if: far_right_coalition_prussia < 50 and ((((ddp_relation >= 60 and ddp_ideology == "Right") or (ddp_relation >= 50 and ddp_ideology == "Moderate") or (ddp_relation >= 40 and ddp_ideology == "Left")) and not lvp_formed) or (((lvp_relation >= 70 and lvp_ideology == "Right") or (lvp_relation >= 60 and lvp_ideology == "Moderate") or (lvp_relation >= 50 and lvp_ideology == "Left")) and lvp_formed))
on-arrival: in_social_liberal_coalition_prussia = 1; was_in_social_liberal_coalition_prussia = 1; liberal_cooperation -= 1 if liberal_parliament == 1; prussia_leader = "Braun"; pro_republic += 3; ddp_relation += 5; lvp_relation += 5; reformist_dissent -= 10; new_middle_ddp += 2; new_middle_lvp += 2; new_middle_spd += 2; spd_prussia = 1

У нас достаточно голосов, чтобы сформировать «<span style="color: #c00000;">социал</span>-[? if not lvp_formed: <span style="color: #D3C24D;">либерал</span>- ?][? if lvp_formed: <span style="color: #FFCC00;">либеральную</span> ?] коалицию» — правительство, состоящее из <span style="color: #c00000;">**СДПГ**</span> и[? if ddp_name == "DDP" and not lvp_formed: <span style="color: #D3C24D;">**Демократической**</span> ?][? if ddp_name == "DStP" and not lvp_formed: <span style="color: #D3C24D;">**Государственной**</span> ?][? if lvp_formed: <span style="color: #FFCC00;">**Либеральной Народной партии**</span> ?] [? if not lvp_formed: (<span style="color: #D3C24D;">**[+ ddp_name +]**</span>) ?][? if lvp_formed: (<span style="color: #FFCC00;">**ЛНП**</span>) ?]! Формирование правого блока <span style="color: #000000;">**[+ z_party_name +]**</span> сделало это возможным.[? if liberal_parliament == 1: Либеральная парламентская фракция оказалась под давлением со стороны <span style="color: #D3C24D;">**[+ ddp_name +]**</span>, действующей по собственному усмотрению. ?]

[? if prussia_leader != "Braun": [+ prussia_leader +] избран министром-президентом Пруссии. ?]


